AzureBlade was somehow amazed that this Predacon actually complimented 
him, and even more that this encounter had went very well. He turned 
to Mistra.

AzureBlade: That was the first time a Predacon told me I was kind! 
What would you do now? Do you want to go to my base and meet the 
others, or would you prefer to stay here for some times? Either way, I 
will be with you.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., Airshadow Nightlight <airly2000@y...> wrote:
> 
>  Kali::
> Kali did a nice smile, She didn't often do that, and said "You're 
right about my spark, but remember this sparks hide more in the deep 
and took time to reach it... I wonder that  your honor sence forbide 
you a treachoury stab... So I'll go first"  Kali walked to the cave's 
entrance she turned and looking to Azure Blade said "You're the most 
kind enemy that I've met, take care, I want to fight with you the next 
time that I see you... So see you next time..."
> Kali left the cave and took off. Soon she was flying towards 
blackfortress
>   warriorazure <wingedwarrior41@h...> wrote: AzureBlade smiled at 
Mistra. He was glad she accepted Kali's 
> conditions.
> 
> AzureBlade: Thank you, Mistra. Now, Kali, I think we have fulfilled 
> your wishes. If you would have the gratefulness to let us go...
